{"tid":2274527,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都話公屋多癲佬，居屋其實都有癲佬","createTime":"2020-11-06T13:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T04:27:10.000Z","uid":140827,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7a1bbc80753f4ebb257c5386eca244168057b5a7","tid":2274527,"uid":140827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/IVIZOEMTQ5AL5FU5SLT7SI7EUM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3XInPxq1uGs2yg8SHSP-fB5aPFRu45CUSgoUvoPJ3DOOOTGL7QYtAyTmw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FIVIZOEMTQ5AL5FU5SLT7SI7EUM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3XInPxq1uGs2yg8SHSP-fB5aPFRu45CUSgoUvoPJ3DOOOTGL7QYtAyTmw&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9gi%2F3qgDO6vJfpFVPRJtUZY%3D&h=fe7859d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201106%2FIVIZOEMTQ5AL5FU5SLT7SI7EUM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3XInPxq1uGs2yg8SHSP-fB5aPFRu45CUSgoUvoPJ3DOOOTGL7QYtAyTmw&h=35515195\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201106/IVIZOEMTQ5AL5FU5SLT7SI7EUM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3XInPxq1uGs2yg8SHSP-fB5aPFRu45CUSgoUvoPJ3DOOOTGL7QYtAyTmw</a><br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳詞指，被告單位位於康盛花園某座31樓，該單位及其毗鄰另一單位因長時間沒交管理費，執達吏奉命收樓，並於2018年5月及7月兩度上門，在兩單位門外張貼告示，通知兩業主即將收樓，並定於同年7月27日正式採取行動。<br />\n當天兩名執達吏在被告住所外，聽到被告在單位內大聲爆粗及不斷拍門，<span class=\"red\">被告大叫「上嚟收管理費？我啱啱先喺青山出嚟！」、「入嚟吖！攞咗嘢招呼你哋，你有膽就入嚟！」</span><br />\n執達吏認為單位內的人甚為瘋狂，單位大門亦被雜物堵塞，無法推開，於是報警求助。及後警方帶備防暴盾到場，警長聞到被告住所內傳出石油氣味。<span class=\"red\">警方於下午12時許企圖打門單位大門，此時有人從單位內擲出冒出火舌的燃燒物，燃燒物爆炸，導致走廊被燻黑。</span>警方旋即疏散居民及嘗試救火。<br />\n當時位於28樓的住戶聽到樓上有人大叫：「仆街！仆你個街！收乜嘢樓！」亦有人大叫「火燭」及疏散住客。<span class=\"red\">不久該名戶主看見僅身穿內褲的被告攬著窗外水管，敲打其窗戶，住戶於是開窗讓被告入屋，被告入屋後即奪門而出。</span><br />\n其後消防到場協助疏散居民，其間在後樓梯發現多名住客，當中包括前臂遭明顯燒傷的被告。被告向消防員透露曾火燒住所，其後向調查警員謂，得悉案發當天被收樓，於是購入天拿水及石油氣罐放火，以圖「一鑊熟」。"},{"pid":"84a8aad1104b9aeb9c3c73c56e0142f934f5c586","tid":2274527,"uid":140827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T13:20:56.000Z","msg":"康盛花園<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76959ed1f82bf934a2f4b20b3972a524f65becb3","tid":2274527,"uid":49634,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T18:10:50.000Z","msg":"寧願燒死自己都唔交管理費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5de2159d86e40c2d5c9958c798be1f23b57321","tid":2274527,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T23:26:01.000Z","msg":"隔離果個單位 直頭有條死屍"},{"pid":"aa8cf37365fe06da0f2f23a3bb1693a9b6050750","tid":2274527,"uid":140513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a5de2159d86e40c2d5c9958c798be1f23b57321","tid":2274527,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T23:26:01.000Z","msg":"隔離果個單位 直頭有條死屍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T23:37:35.000Z","msg":"係骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋主死左好耐都唔知 <br />\n個執達吏真係好大陰影"},{"pid":"e08276651995b72792eb1f983ddbb79ca4e79175","tid":2274527,"uid":227271,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T23:44:06.000Z","msg":"不用分那麼細<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />局屋都係公屋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bba247a407a7d5841adc8d59783d4997114fa10","tid":2274527,"uid":345160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T00:26:53.000Z","msg":"都要睇地區<br />\n康山花園<img src=\"/assets/